<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="faq">Frequently Asked Questions About Wedding DJs</h2>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can a Wedding DJ Take Song Requests?&nbsp;</h3>

<p>Absolutely, and the decision is entirely up to you. Your DJ is available to take requests if that is something you would like. Sometimes, requests can provide useful feedback from the audience and add a fun, interactive element to the party. However, our primary commitment is to you. The DJ will always prioritize your vision and the seamless flow of the musical journey we&#8217;ve planned together, ensuring any request fits the atmosphere and never disrupts the energy on the dance floor.</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What Questions Should I Ask My Wedding DJ?</h3>

<p>Before hiring a wedding DJ, you'll want to ask certain questions to make sure they meet your needs for your special day. Here are some helpful questions to consider:&nbsp;</p>

<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>What is your experience with DJ-ing weddings? How many have you done?</li>
<li>Do you have testimonials from past clients?</li>
<li>Do you have backup equipment in case of technical issues?</li>
<li>How do you handle song requests and do-not-play lists?</li>
<li>Can you make announcements during the event?</li>
<li>Do you offer additional services?</li>
<li>What is your policy on overtime? Is there an additional charge?</li>
<li>How far in advance should we book your services?</li>
<li>What is your cancellation or rescheduling policy?</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How Many Hours Does a DJ Play at a Wedding?</h3>

<p>Our DJ services can be used throughout the entirety of your wedding day, from before the ceremony to the end of the reception. Our wedding package typically includes 4 hours of reception music. Custom packages can be created based on your individual needs.</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Does DJ Misha Perform at Destination Weddings?</h3>

<p>Yes! DJ Misha is available for national and international travel. Whether you're in San Diego or hosting a <a href="/services/destination-wedding-dj/" title="Destination Wedding DJ">destination wedding</a> in a unique location, he can bring the music to you. Reach out to us with details like your wedding location and date, because travel to any destination is possible.</p>

<p>For destination weddings, DJ Misha will take care of all travel booking and equipment rentals that are required for a remote performance, ensuring there is no additional work for you. He will also handle all the coordination between vendors and event planners too, making your destination wedding planning an easy and efficient process.&nbsp;</p>

